
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Ejectuar Crédito Cuenta Contable <br> Epica 2267: PagoPrestamo <br> HU 57003:  POST -  /loans-and-deposits/loan-admin/v1/execute-repayment
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Librería de parámetros <br> lib-java-webflux_core-xrs
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant Idempotencia as Componente de Idempotencia <br> POST: integrity-handler/v1/idempotency/generate
    participant wrapper as Wrapper T24 V2 <br/> OP: Depositoenefectivofase11 <br/> OP: Depositoenefectivofase12
    participant event as AWS EventBridge <br> Componente de Idempotencia 
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> <<Librería de mapeo de errores>>
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - Ejecutar crédito cuenta contable

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: body: <br> currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount, <br> authorizationsNumber, <br> accountGroup, <br> accountMultiple, <br> transactionReference

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros Librería de parámetros caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "LOAN_ADMIN" <br> name: "EXECUTE_REPAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros Librería de parámetros Cahé Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

    else Consulta  parametros en Librería de parámetros / Parameter Store

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros lambda parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "LOAN_ADMIN" <br> name: "EXECUTE_REPAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Librería de parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: value.param-name 

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional Exitosa
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01 

    API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
    Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
    Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> operationHnl <br> operationUsd  <br> caller-service-hnl <br> caller-service-usd

    API->>API: Evaluar request.loanCurrency

    alt If request.loanCurrency == "HNL" 

        API->>API: Selecciona caller-service
        Note over API: $caller-service = const.caller-service-hnl

        API->>API: Selecciona operation
        Note over API: $operation = const.operationHnl

    else  If request.loanCurrency == "USD"

        API->>API: Selecciona caller-service
        Note over API: $caller-service = const.caller-service-usd

        API->>API: Selecciona operation
        Note over API: $operation = const.operationUsd

    else If request.loanCurrency != "HNL" o "USD"

        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        Note left of API: HTTP 422: Tipo de moneda no soportado

    end 

    API->>Idempotencia: Consume API Idempotencia 
    Note right of API: Mapeo de Campos: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: LOAN_ADMIN-product-EXECUTE_REPAYMENT <br> "methodVersion": "1.0" <br> dataPayload: {request}

    Idempotencia->>API: Response API Idempotencia 
    Note left of Idempotencia: Response: data {status, code, tittle, detail, correlation-id}
    
    API->>API: Evalua response API Idempotencia

    alt If data.code != 0

        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        Note left of API: HTTP 422: Transacción efectuada previamente

    else If data.code == 0

        alt If request.loanCurrency == "HNL" 

            API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase11
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> header:  caller-service = $caller-service <br> body: <br> operation = $operation <br> OfsFunction.messageId = header.Correlation-Id <br> OfsFunction.noOfAuth = request.noOfAuth <br> gTRANSACTION.atribute.g = request.accountGroup <br> mTRANSACTION.atribute.m = request.accountMultiple <br> DepositAmount = request.paymentAmount

            API->>wrapper: Consume Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase11
            Note right of API:  header: caller-service, <br> body: operation, OfsFunction.messageId, <br> OfsFunction.noOfAuth, gTRANSACTION.atribute.g, <br> mTRANSACTION.atribute.m, DepositAmount

            wrapper->>API: Response Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase11
            Note over wrapper: Response: <br> success, data

            API->>API: Evalúa Response Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase11

            alt If success == true 

                API->>API: Construye response API
                Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno campos del response Wrapper

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: $caller-service <br> payload: {request} <br> transactionStatus: success 

                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

            else If success != true 

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: $caller-service <br> payload: {request} <br> transactionStatus: timeOut

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422 + wrapper.mensajeError

            end

        else  request.loanCurrency == "USD" 

            API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase12
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> header:  caller-service = $caller-service <br> body: <br> operation = $operation <br> OfsFunction.messageId = header.Correlation-Id <br> OfsFunction.noOfAuth = request.noOfAuth <br> CurrencyDeposited = request.loanCurrency <br> gTRANSACTION.atribute.g = request.accountGroup <br> mTRANSACTION.atribute.m = request.accountMultiple <br> DepositAmount = request.paymentAmount 

            API->>wrapper: Consume Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase12
            Note right of API: header: caller-service, <br> body: operation, OfsFunction.messageId, <br> OfsFunction.noOfAuth, CurrencyDeposited, <br> gTRANSACTION.atribute.g, mTRANSACTION.atribute.m, <br> DepositAmount

            wrapper->>API: Response Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase12
            Note over wrapper: Response: <br> success, data

            API->>API: Evalúa Response Wrapper T24 - OP: Depositoenefectivofase12

            alt If success == true 

                API->>API: Construye response API
                Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno campos del response Wrapper

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: $caller-service <br>  request: {request} <br> Transaccion: success 

                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

            else If success != true 

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API:Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: $caller-service <br>  request: {request} <br> Transaccion: TimeOut

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
                
                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
                
                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422 + wrapper.mensajeError

            end

        end

    end 

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API